{"title_page": "Step into My World EP", "text_new": "{{unreferenced|date=October 2008}}\n{{Infobox album\n| name         = Step into My World EP\n| type         = ep\n| artist       = [[Hurricane No. 1|Hurricane #1]]\n| cover        = stepintomyworldep.jpg\n| released     = October 1997\n| recorded     = \n| venue        = \n| studio       = \n| genre        = [[Britpop]], [[Trip Hop]], [[Breakbeat]]\n| length       = 3:59 (Perfecto Radio Edit)<br>5:02 (Original Version)\n| label        = [[Creation Records]]\n| producer     = [[Stephen Harris (producer)|Stephen Harris]], [[Andy Bell (musician)|Andy Bell]], [[Paul Oakenfold]], [[Steve Osborne]]\n| prev_title   = [[Hurricane No.&nbsp;1 (album)|Hurricane #1]]\n| prev_year    = 1997\n| year         = 1997\n| next_title   = [[Only the Strongest Will Survive]]\n| next_year    = 1999\n}}\n'''''Step into My World EP''''' is an EP by the British rock band [[Hurricane_No._1|Hurricane #1]], released in 1997. It features the Perfecto remix by [[Paul Oakenfold]] and [[Steve Osborne]]. It reached top 20 in the UK Singles Charts. \n\n==Track listing==\n\n*CD <small>CRESCD 276</small>\n# \"Step Into My World (The Perfecto Radio Edit)\" \n# \"Step Into My World\" \n# \"If You Think It's Easy\"\n# \"Never Mind the Rain\" \n\n*CD - Mixes <small>CRESCD 276X</small>\n# \"Step Into My World (The Perfecto Mix)\"\n# \"Step Into My World (FC Kahuna Mix)\"\n# \"Step Into My World (The Perfecto Dub)\"\n# \"Step Into My World (Get It Together Mix)\"\n\n*7\" <small>CRE 276</small>\n# \"Step Into My World (The Perfecto Radio Edit)\" \n# \"If You Think It's Easy\"\n\n==Personnel==\n\"Step Into My World Ep\"<br/>\n1, Remix produced and mixed by [[Paul Oakenfold]] and [[Steve Osborne]] <br/>\nRemix engineer Danton Supple<br/>\nRemix programming - Ben Hillier for 140dB<br/>\n2, 3, 4, Produced by [[Stephen Harris (producer)|Stephen Harris]] and [[Andy Bell (musician)|Andy Bell]]<br/>\nEngineered and mixed by [[Stephen Harris (producer)|Stephen Harris]]<br/>\nAll songs written by [[Andy Bell (musician)|Andy Bell]] (Creation Songs)<br/>\nPhotography by Tim Page<br/>\nDesign by Phantom Industries\n\n[[Category:1997 EPs]]\n[[Category:Creation Records EPs]]\n", "text_old": "{{Distinguish|Step Into My World}}{{unreferenced|date=October 2008}}\n{{Infobox album\n| name         = Step into My World EP\n| type         = ep\n| artist       = [[Hurricane No. 1|Hurricane #1]]\n| cover        = stepintomyworldep.jpg\n| released     = October 1997\n| recorded     = \n| venue        = \n| studio       = \n| genre        = [[Britpop]], [[Trip Hop]], [[Breakbeat]]\n| length       = 3:59 (Perfecto Radio Edit)<br>5:02 (Original Version)\n| label        = [[Creation Records]]\n| producer     = [[Stephen Harris (producer)|Stephen Harris]], [[Andy Bell (musician)|Andy Bell]], [[Paul Oakenfold]], [[Steve Osborne]]\n| prev_title   = [[Hurricane No.&nbsp;1 (album)|Hurricane #1]]\n| prev_year    = 1997\n| year         = 1997\n| next_title   = [[Only the Strongest Will Survive]]\n| next_year    = 1999\n}}\n'''''Step into My World EP''''' is an EP by the British rock band [[Hurricane_No._1|Hurricane #1]], released in 1997. It features the Perfecto remix by [[Paul Oakenfold]] and [[Steve Osborne]]. It reached top 20 in the UK Singles Charts.\n\n==Track listing==\n\n*CD <small>CRESCD 276</small>\n# \"Step Into My World (The Perfecto Radio Edit)\" \n# \"Step Into My World\" \n# \"If You Think It's Easy\"\n# \"Never Mind the Rain\" \n\n*CD - Mixes <small>CRESCD 276X</small>\n# \"Step Into My World (The Perfecto Mix)\"\n# \"Step Into My World (FC Kahuna Mix)\"\n# \"Step Into My World (The Perfecto Dub)\"\n# \"Step Into My World (Get It Together Mix)\"\n\n*7\" <small>CRE 276</small>\n# \"Step Into My World (The Perfecto Radio Edit)\" \n# \"If You Think It's Easy\"\n\n==Personnel==\n\"Step Into My World Ep\"<br/>\n1, Remix produced and mixed by [[Paul Oakenfold]] and [[Steve Osborne]] <br/>\nRemix engineer Danton Supple<br/>\nRemix programming -